        I'm a Software Engineer at Quaisr in London, working across frontend and backend on an agentic AI product. Previously, I spent three years at LoveCare, a healthcare platform in Indonesia, where I built production features and explored how AI can improve healthcare workflows. I also hold an MSc in Data Science and AI with Distinction from the University of Liverpool.
    </p> -->

</div>
